            <h2>Our PSA</h2>
            <p>
              <strong>This is an important public safety announcement. Please, read as everyone under the age of 18 is affected by this.</strong>
            </p>
            <p>Following certain controversies, we would like to reinforce our policies and rules that protect everyone, especially users who are under the age of 18. This applies to all AT Products LLC-owned/based Discord servers.</p>
            <p>The following documents will be discussed: </p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a href="https://discord.com/terms">https://discord.com/terms</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://discord.com/guidelines">https://discord.com/guidelines</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://atproducts.xyz/discord">https://atproducts.xyz/discord</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p></p>
            <p>As we all know, in the U.S., anybody below the age of 18 is legally considered a minor and still a child. Please keep that definition in mind, as it will be discussed multiple times. Anybody who has an attraction to a minor is considered a pedophile, which will also be discussed below.</p>
            <p>Please note that we take these policies seriously. If you have any concerns or questions, please do not hesitate to let me know.</p>
            <p>If you find any of these rule breaks, notify an staff member immediately. If you are curious about how we handle these situations, scroll below.</p>
            <p>The following rules/policies are in place:</p>
            <h3 id="users-under-the-age-of-13">Users under the age of 13</h3>
            <p>Any users found (or suspected) to be under the age of 13 will be banned immediately as per the <a href="https://discord.com/terms#2">Discord Terms of Service</a>, no exceptions. </p>
            <h3 id="users-under-the-age-of-18">Users under the age of 18</h3>
            <p>Once again, in the U.S., anybody below the age of 18 is legally considered a minor, and anybody who has an attraction to a minor is considered a pedophile. Anybody to be found (or suspected) of conducting pedophilic behavior or who has a previous history of such behavior will be banned immediately, following the <a href="https://discord.com/guidelines">Discord Community Guidelines</a> and <a href="https://atproducts.xyz/discord/">ATP Discord Rules</a>
            </p>
            <p>The following citations define the rule in place here in CodingHome v2, the first one being the <a href="https://discord.com/guidelines">Discord Community Guidelines</a>: </p>
            <blockquote>
              <p>Do not solicit, share, or make any attempt to distribute content that depicts, promotes, or attempts to normalize child sexual abuse. Also, do not post content or engage in conduct that in any way sexualizes children. This includes real as well as manipulated media, animation (such as lolicon), and any type of digital creation (note that this includes AI-generated media).</p>
            </blockquote>
            <p>And the second one being from the <a href="https://atproducts.xyz/discord/">ATP Discord Rules</a>, please note that it also shares on how we enforce it: </p>
            <blockquote>
              <p>Zoophilia, pedophilia, necrophilia, and any other forms of illegal behavior with/without paraphilias, such as exploitation of minors/animals, will not be tolerated under any circumstances. Any such activity will result in an instant ban if mentioned in any form and may be reported to Discord staff, law enforcement authorities, and/or the National Center for Exploited and Missing Children, respectively. Any other sexual attractions (even if they are not necessarily illegal) shall not be shared and will also result in a punishment (dependent on the Server's policy) if mentioned in any form.</p>
            </blockquote>
            <p>
