              <li>Report the inappropriate behavior in any means necessary, either by direct messaging us or pinging us. </li>
              <li>Please show evidence of how the behavior is taking place, either by screenshots or screen recordings.</li>
              <li>We will handle it from here and out. We will notify you if any action is taken and what it will be.</li>
            </ol>
            <h3 id="what-we-do">What we do</h3>
