              <li>We will investigate the evidence of what happened or what we currently have.</li>
              <li>If the behavior is indeed what we think it is, an instant ban will occur <strong>with zero chance to appeal, with zero warnings</strong>, and we will report all messages referring to such. </li>
              <li>We will make a <a href="https://report.cybertip.org/">https://report.cybertip.org/</a> report, which is owned by the US National Center for Missing &amp; Exploited Children. </li>
              <li>Contact Discord Staff via email or any other way necessary.</li>
